# Hub UI — production source of truth

## Do not

- Re-add legacy `ToolCard` / `StoreTab` / `hub-spectrum.css` (removed).
- Duplicate badge icons outside `src/lib/badge-registry.ts`.
- Re-add multi-variant hub-ui pickers without explicit user request.

## Production

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Hub grid card | `src/features/hub/HubToolCard.tsx` |
| Hub table | `src/features/store/TableView.tsx` |
| Badges / filter icons | `src/lib/badge-registry.ts` |
| Tool Links (System) | `src/features/overview/ToolLinksTable.tsx` |
| Shell header | `src/components/sales-shell/AppTabHeader.tsx` |
| Filters | `src/components/sales-shell/FilterBar.tsx` |

## Design Template tab

- System → **Design Template** — locked decision log only (`locked-decisions.ts`). No V1–V5 pickers or mock previews.

## Checks before push

- `pnpm run lint` · `pnpm run deadcode` · `pnpm run build`
